<div id="Item_0" class="PageTitle"><div class="Options"></div><h1>[Civil Affairs] Forgotten Fronts - Operation Dragoon '44</h1></div>

<div id="Discussion_1805" class="Item ItemDiscussion">
    <div class="Discussion">
        <div class="Item-Header DiscussionHeader">
            <div class="AuthorWrap">
