                <span class="MItem"> <span title="Edited April 14, 2015 12:53AM by 1Lt. Hampbell [Ret.]." class="DateUpdated">edited April 2015</span> </span>                 <span class="MItem Category"> in <a href="../../categories/civil-announcements">Civil Announcements</a></span>             </div>
